  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/gaming/\" rel=\"tag\">游戏产品</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/12/19/early-valve-steam-machine-easily-torn-down-by-team-ifixit/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://hss-prod.hss.aol.com/hss/storage/adam/76bda15316fd19f7ec93b6f6719aa153/ifixit-steam-machine-2013-12-19-01.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n虽说测试版 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/steammachine\">Steam Machine</a> 只有区区 300 台，但拆机大师 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/ifixit\">iFixit</a> 还是想方设法为自己搞到了其中之一。而这一台显然不是拿来玩的，既然入了他们的法眼，难免要被开膛破肚一番。就拆解结果来看，Steam Machine 可谓非常之好修，在常规的修理简易性打分中它拿到了 9 分的高分。不过话说这款产品本来就和其它主机不同，它类似小型 PC 加可更换零件的设计完全就是为了让人改造而设的。<br />\n<br />\n打开机体后，iFixit 发现了 Zotac NVIDIA GTX 780 显卡（3GB）、1TB Seagate hybrid SSHD 硬盘、16GB DDR3 内存、3.6GHz Intel Core i5-4570 处理器和 450W 的电源。至于控制器也十分容易打开，无论是其可定制性还是按键数量都令人满意。要说不足的话，iFixit 认为内存比较难拆，除此之外电线排列也有点复杂。想看完整拆解的话，就去来源中瞧瞧吧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/12/19/early-valve-steam-machine-easily-torn-down-by-team-ifixit/\">Engadget</a><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://www.ifixit.com/Teardown/Steam+Machine+Teardown/20473\" target=\"_blank\">iFixit</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/12/19/early-valve-steam-machine-easily-torn-down-by-team-ifixit/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20792235/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/12/19/early-valve-steam-machine-easily-torn-down-by-team-ifixit/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
